match_description: Non‑tech founder meets an engineer who can own the tech stack—idea + coding = complete team.

profiles.raw_input: Hi there! I'm Jessica Morgan, founder of HealthTrack, a digital health platform that helps patients track and manage their chronic conditions. I have a strong background in healthcare administration and product strategy, but I need a technical partner who can build and lead our tech development. I've validated the idea with potential users and have some initial funding, but I need someone who can translate our vision into a working product. Looking to connect with experienced engineers who are passionate about healthcare innovation and interested in joining an early-stage startup as a technical co-founder.

personal.name: Jessica Morgan
personal.headline: Founder of HealthTrack - Digital Health Platform

roles.title: Founder & CEO
highlights: Validated product idea with 50+ potential users
Built relationships with healthcare providers for pilot program

roles.title: Senior Product Manager
highlights: Led digital transformation initiatives for patient management
Managed cross-functional teams to implement new healthcare software
Identified key pain points in patient experience journey

profiles.extra_notes: Specifically looking for a technical co-founder with healthcare experience. Have MVP wireframes ready to discuss.

profiles.raw_input: Hello, I'm Alex Chen, a full-stack developer with 8+ years of experience building scalable web applications. I've been tech lead at several startups and have expertise in JavaScript, React, Node.js, and cloud infrastructure. I've always been passionate about healthcare technology and its potential to improve lives. After years of working for others, I'm looking to join an early-stage venture as a technical co-founder where I can build and own the entire tech stack. I'm particularly interested in healthcare solutions and would love to meet founders who have domain expertise but need a technical partner to bring their vision to life.

personal.name: Alex Chen
personal.headline: Senior Full-Stack Engineer seeking CTO role

roles.title: Lead Software Engineer
highlights: Led development of HIPAA-compliant patient portal
Architected scalable backend services handling millions of records
Reduced infrastructure costs by 40% through optimization

roles.title: Senior Full-Stack Developer
highlights: Built real-time data visualization platform from scratch
Mentored junior developers and conducted code reviews

profiles.extra_notes: Ready to commit full-time to the right venture. Particularly interested in healthcare tech that makes a meaningful impact. Can lead technical architecture and build MVP rapidly.
